               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner</hi>. I had some silk in my pocket, and wanted some cotton matched—I wanted some silk finer than what I had got in my pocket—I do not know what there was besides—I had been on business and taken part of several glasses of brandy and water, and when I am in that way do not know what I do—I have been handcuffed to my bed ever since I have been here—I was confined once before—my friends live in the country—I am a tailor, and live at Chelsea—I have been better for some time than I was, but a little refreshment produces excitement in me.</p>
